            "readonly": false,
            "desc": "Publish a new trading insight and receive seller ASA for proof-of-ownership.\nPurpose: Allocate unique listing ID and link IPFS content permanently on-chain.\nActions: 1. Increment next_listing_id counter \u2192 allocate new listing ID. 2. Call itxn.AssetConfig to mint one ASA with:    - INSIGHT token name, Mercator Insight asset name, IpfsHash as URL.    - Seller as manager + reserve + freeze + clawback (seller controls proof token).    - Fee=1000 micro-Algo. 3. Store Listing struct in boxes: {price, seller, ipfs_hash, asa_id}. 4. Increment counter for next invocation. 5. Return listing_id to caller (frontend caches this).",
